at mismatch:** Initial proof used `### AC1:` (h3) headers instead of `## AC 1:` (h2) format expected by `validateProofQuality`. Required proof rewrite.","-- **Verification gaps:** AC6 (retryable=false on second failure) — parser always throws `retryable: true`, caller handles retry semantics. Accepted per design intent.","-- Coverage run 3 times with different grep filters — could have captured once and filtered locally.","-","-## Token Report — verification","-- Total tool calls: 16","-- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 2, Grep: 3, Write: 1","-- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test | tail -80` (~80 lines), `vitest --reporter=verbose` (~40 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)","-- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads","-- Redundant operations: Coverage command run 3 times with different grep filters"]}],"originalFile":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-03\n\n### 6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing — create-story (2026-04-03T03:58)\n\n- **epic-6 status stale**: sprint-status.yaml showed `epic-6: backlog` but `6-1` is `done`. Fixed by orchestrator.\n- **No config.yaml found**: `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` does not exist. Used defaults.\n- **All ACs test-provable**: Every AC verifiable by build + tests. No runtime or environment needed.\n- **Ajv dependency unknown**: Dev agent should check and install if missing.\n\n## Token Report — create-story\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 8, Glob: 4, Grep: 2, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git log --oneline -10` (~10 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 10 total reads (no file read 3+ times)\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing — dev-story (2026-04-03T04:04)\n\n- **Code quality concern:** `buildAllUnknownVerdict` in workflow-engine.ts mirrors `buildUnknownOutput` in evaluator.ts in shape/intent, but one returns string and other returns object. Could be unified but story says not to modify evaluator.ts.\n- **Branch coverage gap:** Lines 85/87 (`??` fallback) and line 152 (`passed === 0` check) at 86.95% branch coverage. 100% line/function coverage acceptable.\n- No build, dependency, or regression issues.\n\n## Token Report — dev-story\n- Total tool calls: 25\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 8, Edit: 11, Grep: 2, Write: 3, Glob: 3\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~30 lines), `npx vitest run --coverage` (~20 lines), `npm run build` (~20 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 10 total reads (no file read 3+ times)\n- Redundant operations: One re-read of workflow-engine.test.ts, two coverage grep attempts\n\n### 6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing — code-review (2026-04-03T04:08)\n\n- **HIGH fixed:** `validateVerdict` returned mutable reference to input — fixed with deep clone\n- **MEDIUM fixed:** `VerdictParseError` missing `Object.setPrototypeOf` for reliable `instanceof`\n- **MEDIUM fixed:** Inconsistent `additionalProperties` in schema (score/evidence were `false`, top-level was `true`)\n- **MEDIUM fixed:** Branch coverage gap improved with 5 new tests (28→33 tests)\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `buildAllUnknownVerdict` takes `WorkItem[]` but only uses `.length`\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `parseVerdict` always throws `retryable: true` (stateless) — spec says different values per call count but parser can't track this. Engine handles it correctly.\n- Coverage: 96.8% overall, all 160 files above 80% floor.\n\n## Token Report — code-review\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 8, Edit: 5, Grep: 3, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `npm run build` (~10 lines), `git diff --name-only` (~15 lines)\n- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads (no file read 3+ times)\n- Redundant operations: one redundant grep for coverage output\n\n### 6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing — verification (2026-04-03T04:14)\n\n- **AGENTS.md stale:** `codeharness verify` initially failed because AGENTS.md was missing entries for `evaluator.ts` and `verdict-parser.ts`. Fixed by adding Blind Evaluator (Epic 6) section.\n- **Proof format mismatch:** Initial proof used `### AC1:` (h3) headers instead of `## AC 1:` (h2) format expected by `validateProofQuality`. Required proof rewrite.\n- **Verification gaps:** AC6 (retryable=false on second failure) — parser always throws `retryable: true`, caller handles retry semantics. Accepted per design intent.\n- Coverage run 3 times with different grep filters — could have captured once and filtered locally.\n\n## Token Report — verification\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 2, Grep: 3, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test | tail -80` (~80 lines), `vitest --reporter=verbose` (~40 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Coverage command run 3 times with different grep filters\n"}}
